item.title: Hello, I'm George; a seasoned storyteller with a knack for video, photography, and voiceovers. I started creating videos when I was 11 years old. After having several businesses hire me for small works, I decided to get back into video as a profession. Since May 2015, I have been helping small businesses with their marketing, content creation, and branding.
